OL,2,MCognitive biases: The bugs, features
OL,4,Mand zero‑days of the human mind
OL,6,CKarolina Czarna
OL,7,CSat 10:00-10:30
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GOur brains are extraordinary: fast,
OL,11,Gintuitive and endlessly creative, but
OL,12,Gthey also come with quirks, shortcuts
OL,13,Gand predictable bugs. These “cognitive
OL,14,Gbiases” shape everything from the food
OL,15,Gwe order to the technologies we build,
OL,16,Goften without us noticing. In this
OL,17,Gtalk, we’ll explore some of the most
OL,18,Gsurprising and entertaining biases
OL,19,Gthat influence our everyday decisions
OL,20,Gand what they reveal about how humans
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
